KANG SI-YEOL MEMBUNUHNYA DI LAPANGAN!

496
00:41:14.889 --> 00:41:16.766
-Kang Si-yeol!
-Kang Si-yeol!

497
00:41:20.395 --> 00:41:22.105
TAHAN NAPAS ANDA
