514
00:43:28.731 --> 00:43:30.608
BANDARA INCHEON MENJADI LIAR BAGI KANG SI-YEOL

515
00:43:33.528 --> 00:43:35.655
Uji Coba Terbuka Daeheung Citizens FC

516
00:43:35.780 --> 00:43:36.864
