517
00:43:40.576 --> 00:43:42.495
Hei, Woo-seok.

518
00:43:44.080 --> 00:43:45.331
Halo, Pelatih.

519
00:43:45.414 --> 00:43:46.624
Ya, hai.

520
00:43:47.708 --> 00:43:48.876
